OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,FITV News' Emma Sweeney spoke to the
OL,8,Fwoman who was raped and abused by
OL,9,FMuhammad Nasir.
OL,11,FA woman who was raped and abducted by
OL,12,Fa taxi driver in Manchester city
OL,13,Fcentre has urged others not to suffer
OL,14,Fin silence.
OL,16,FTaxi driver Muhammad Nasir of
OL,17,FStockport Road, Ashton-under-Lyne, was
OL,18,Fjailed for 12 years after being found
OL,19,Fguilty of abducting and raping a 20-
OL,20,Fyear-old university student.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
