PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,FIn July 2021 he picked her up outside
OL,8,Fa nightclub in Manchester city centre.
OL,10,FRecalling the night, the survivor, who
OL,11,Fasked to remain anonymous, said she
OL,12,Fwas out with her friends when she
OL,13,Fdecided to head home.
OL,15,FShe said: "We danced, drank a little
OL,16,Fbit more, caught up with each other
OL,17,Fand then in the early hours of the
OL,18,Fmorning, I said I'm going to leave
OL,19,Fnow. Just because no other reason
OL,20,Fother than I was tired."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,FAt around 2am, she began looking for a
OL,8,Ftaxi when Nasir pulled up.
OL,10,FShe said: "I just got in the back like
OL,11,FI normally would. It was quite a
OL,12,Fnormal start to a taxi ride."
OL,14,FBut Nasir quickly went off route and
OL,15,Fthe journey, which should have taken
OL,16,Fjust 20 minutes, turned into a three
OL,17,Fhour ordeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,FNasir, who had logged off from his
OL,8,Ftaxi system, drove the woman away from
OL,9,Fher intended route and raped her in
OL,10,FChorlton. She did not arrive home
OL,11,Funtil nearly 5:30 am.
OL,13,FShe said: "I think at the time, it was
OL,14,Fmore of a case of flight, fight or
OL,15,Ffreeze. I think my subconscious
OL,16,Factually realised before I did."
OL,18,FIn the days following the rape, she
OL,19,Ftold those around her about the
OL,20,Fincident, got specialist support, and
OL,21,Freported Nasir to the police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,FNasir denied any wrongdoing, claiming
OL,8,Fthe encounter was consensual and even
OL,9,Falleging the victim had assaulted him.
OL,11,FHowever, Judge Suzanne Goddard KC
OL,12,Fsaid: "This was a horrendous incident
OL,13,Fin which I am satisfied, to the
OL,14,Fcriminal standard, that you
OL,15,Fdeliberately picked up a clearly
OL,16,Fdrunken lone female with the intention
OL,17,Fof taking sexual advantage of her.
OL,19,F"I regard you as a dangerous and
OL,20,Fpredatory sex offender."
OL,26,@tD@GOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
