FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,FFive years on, she says she's been
OL,8,Fable to move on thanks to her attacker
OL,9,Ffacing justice and is now encouraging
OL,10,Fother survivors to come forward.
OL,12,FShe said: "I'm really good in myself
OL,13,Fand I think I've come a long way.
OL,15,F"When something like this happens to
OL,16,Fanyone, no matter what it is, any sort
OL,17,Fof assault, sexual assault or sexual
OL,18,Fviolence, often I think you can feel
OL,19,Fquite alone and isolated. You're not.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,F"It's not an embarrassing thing, it
OL,8,Fshould be spoken about."
OL,10,FThe CEO of Manchester Rape Crisis
OL,11,FAlison Lloyd sat down with Katie
OL,12,FWalderman and Gamal Fahnbulleh to talk
OL,13,Fabout the incident and the support
OL,14,Favailable for survivors.
OL,16,FHer words come as Greater Manchester
OL,17,FPolice and support groups continue to
OL,18,Furge people to come forward, seek help
OL,19,Fand report offences, assuring them
OL,20,Fthey will be listened to and supported.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
