OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779084318
OL,3,CWoman who was raped by taxi driver
OL,4,Cencourages survivors to report
OL,5,Cattackers
OL,7,FDetective Constable James Adams
OL,8,Fpraised the survivor's courage and
OL,9,Fresilience. He said: "Her
OL,10,Fdetermination to ensure that what
OL,11,Fhappened to her does not define her is
OL,12,Fremarkable. Rape is one of the most
OL,13,Fserious and devastating crimes a
OL,14,Fperson can experience.
OL,16,F"Greater Manchester Police will not
OL,17,Ftolerate sexual violence in any form,
OL,18,Fand we will always work to hold
OL,19,Foffenders to account."
OL,26,@qD@VOU{D@VO]
